<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-05-11T04:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-05-11T04:00:00-05:00" n="487" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d487">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">751G.00/5–1154: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Chargé at Saigon</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MCR1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">McClintock</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi></seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Saigon</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1954-05-11T17:00:00+08:00">May 11, 1954—5
                                    p.m.</date></dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>2333. Sent Geneva 84, repeated information Paris 813. I trust <gloss target="#t_USDel1">USDel</gloss> Geneva will keep a weather eye
                                out for possibility that, in framing military provisions of an
                                armistice, Communists will write in a clause forbidding either side
                                to improve its military posture, as for example by construction of
                                air bases or training indigenous troops <pb facs="0796" n="770" xml:id="pg_770"/> by foreign means. Unless we are careful they
                                could effectively spike any <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss>
                                program for training of, and operational planning in, Vietnamese
                                National Army.</p>
                            <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_MCR1"><hi rend="smallcaps">McClintock</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>